Class ContentBlockType1

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.xamoom.android.mapping.ContentBlocks.ContentBlock
      • com.xamoom.android.mapping.ContentBlocks.ContentBlockType1

  • public class ContentBlockType1
extends ContentBlock
    Used for mapping Audio contentBlocks received from the xamoom-cloud-api. You have to implement your own music player to stream the file. The fileId is only a URL pointing to the file in our cloud.
